These are the source files for the IUCr LaTeX macro package.

iucr.cls:          the class file containing all the macros
template.ltx:      a skeleton template file used to construct an article for
                   submission to an IUCr journal
documentation.ltx: a documentation and test file
fig1.ps:           a small PostScript figure included in the documentation
                   as an example
iucr.bib:          a BibTeX bibliography file for the documentation
iucr.bst:          the IUCr BibTeX bibliography style file
